-- MOVES-Tilney Bestinvest hires David Cummins from European Wealth
-- 
-- Wed Sep 17, 2014 09:47AM EDT
-- None



Sept 17 (Reuters) - Tilney Bestinvest, a UK-based investment and financial planning firm, said it appointed David Cummins as director of financial planning as it expands its regional financial planning presence.

The firm said Cummins will be based in its new office at Maidstone and will report to Richard Dawes, managing director of financial planning at the firm. Cummins joins from European Wealth <EWGE.L>, where he was the senior financial adviser.